  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the rest meat and cook until it is browned on all sides.",
    "Add the chopped carrots and potatoes, and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the vegetable broth, tomato paste, thyme, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "Add the black olives and continue to simmer for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
